Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.02,0:00:04.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,布里塔尼亚少年  鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.18,0:00:06.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拥有两个力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.34,0:00:08.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一个是Geass
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.97,0:00:12.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对任何对手都能下令使其绝对服从的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.44,0:00:14.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一个是黑色骑士团
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.70,0:00:19.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为破坏父亲统治的布里塔尼亚的他自己的军队
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.13,0:00:24.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修借ZERO这个代号行动起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.28,0:00:26.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了替母亲报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.33,0:00:31.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有为了创造妹妹娜娜莉能幸福生活的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.61,0:00:35.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这行动会导致怎样的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.58,0:00:38.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在谁也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.64,0:02:14.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fad(600,0)\pos(424,395)}STAGE 12
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.64,0:02:14.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fad(600,0)\pos(424,430)}京都来的使者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.90,0:02:18.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由于总督的作战  日本解放战线几乎是毁灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.44,0:02:22.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,逃亡中的成员也接连被抓获
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.45,0:02:23.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这算是揶揄吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.33,0:02:26.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在我军正苦恼着如何重新振作的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.81,0:02:28.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我并没有这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.67,0:02:31.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其实难道不是占领后的政策有问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.94,0:02:34.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,11区的地下铁路网  矿山  矿道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.01,0:02:35.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么就这么放置着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.65,0:02:39.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,平民区的户籍管理和地产的所有权还是这么的暧昧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.22,0:02:42.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,反政府势力的温床就这么被放置着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.32,0:02:47.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个  地下铁几乎是遍布全国
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.61,0:02:50.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,管理想要覆盖到租界以外的地方的话  预算实在是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.52,0:02:53.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即使明白这会成为恐怖分子的据点和逃跑路线还这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.04,0:02:55.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这是克洛维斯殿下的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.39,0:03:00.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  太过强硬会造成内乱状态
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.71,0:03:03.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,会给中华联邦可趁之机
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.69,0:03:04.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是已经给了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.56,0:03:07.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO的势力正在慢慢集结力量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.28,0:03:08.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,事务次官
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.56,0:03:10.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在内政省的管理下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.35,0:03:14.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有对这个地区进行自治的11区的代表是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.32,0:03:17.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被称为NAC的组织
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.16,0:03:22.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在前几天的作战中抓住了NAC的把柄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.48,0:03:23.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但资料被掩埋了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.41,0:03:26.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但有嫌疑是毫无疑问的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.96,0:03:28.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要控制住他们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.45,0:03:32.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  名门和财阀的集合体
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.27,0:03:34.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经是历史的遗物了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.49,0:03:36.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.58,0:03:37.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这只不过是传闻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.44,0:03:39.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,根本没有证据
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.70,0:03:41.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果压制了他们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.85,0:03:43.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就无法恢复11区的经济
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.31,0:03:46.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对本国的征税也会有影响
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.29,0:03:52.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且编号住民自己照顾自己是帝国的大方针
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.76,0:03:54.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么黑色骑士团的搜索呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.07,0:03:56.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从留下的挖掘机械资料来看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.96,0:04:00.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然证明成田的事是ZERO的所为
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.43,0:04:03.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但找不到团员尸骸以外的线索
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.43,0:04:04.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能对京都出手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.22,0:04:06.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又无法把ZERO逼入绝境
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.39,0:04:08.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.05,0:04:10.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从结果上来看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.85,0:04:11.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是所谓的无能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.13,0:04:15.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到布里塔尼亚的皇女竟能做到如此地步
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.21,0:04:18.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,解放战线已经分裂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.40,0:04:20.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,日本统一的力量之灯火已经消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.86,0:04:22.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说还太早
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.04,0:04:24.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说还在逃亡中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.43,0:04:26.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但藤堂还健在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.57,0:04:27.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那有什么用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.90,0:04:30.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,听说连无赖·改也失去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.47,0:04:31.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没有希望了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.01,0:04:33.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有希望啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.45,0:04:35.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,黑色骑士团吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.27,0:04:37.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,红莲二式也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.22,0:04:40.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,枢木朱雀救出事件以来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.28,0:04:41.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,您对ZERO很热衷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.76,0:04:45.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由于特拉法尔加战役的败北
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.76,0:04:50.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[1805年,在纳尔逊指挥下的英国舰队于直布罗陀海峡西北的特拉\N法尔加角击败法国和西班牙联合舰队的海战。挫败了拿破仑登陆\N英国本土的作战计划。英国掌握了制海权，纳尔逊战死。]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.73,0:04:50.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,伊丽莎白三世被革命势力包围在爱丁堡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.12,0:04:52.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.47,0:04:55.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}当时布里塔尼亚公镇守在殖民地美洲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.86,0:04:57.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6}也就是我们现在的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.98,0:05:12.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  一脸复杂的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.56,0:05:13.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,便秘？ 宿醉？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.61,0:05:15.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.62,0:05:17.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么是鲁路修不在  感到寂寞了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.66,0:05:23.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说呢  卡莲也一起缺席  又是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.98,0:05:28.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真悠闲啊  世界却正为前几天的成田事件而混乱不已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.20,0:05:31.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀也因为这事今天请假
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.92,0:05:32.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.51,0:05:36.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但我只是觉得鲁路和卡莲的事更成问题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.02,0:05:39.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真好啊  莎莉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.76,0:05:40.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是喜欢你的这种性格
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.99,0:05:43.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请别拿我寻开心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.06,0:05:47.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说  你直说不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.98,0:05:49.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.25,0:05:52.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样不行的  这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.58,0:05:53.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为  如果
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.88,0:05:55.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被拒绝了怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.07,0:05:58.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定连朋友也做不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.83,0:06:03.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也用不着  笑得那么夸张吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.62,0:06:09.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是很开心啊  在这个地方  还有我们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.66,0:06:10.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.38,0:06:13.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是还是做好一点觉悟的好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.33,0:06:16.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不变的事物在哪儿都是不存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.46,0:06:21.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  别这么认真嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.22,0:06:25.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果无论如何都想知道的话  干脆去问本人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.62,0:06:28.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  那边情况怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.03,0:06:31.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁…鲁路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.86,0:06:32.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天不是休息吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.08,0:06:34.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉稍微有点发烧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.38,0:06:37.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnDFPHSGothic-W5\fe128\fs25\b1\alpha&H15&}咲{\r}世子白天有点事要做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.52,0:06:39.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.82,0:06:41.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小娜娜的情况好点了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.65,0:06:42.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.07,0:06:44.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,会长  那个文件
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.79,0:06:45.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  在那儿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.81,0:06:48.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,分发到各学年的各个班级上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.54,0:06:49.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是  是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.73,0:06:51.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还是这么会差遣人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.07,0:06:53.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拥有能干的部下真是幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.20,0:06:54.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,部下？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.31,0:06:57.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  还真是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.12,0:07:00.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  会长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.95,0:07:03.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样对心脏不好啊  你那种
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.63,0:07:05.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  门票
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.29,0:07:08.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.47,0:07:10.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.27,0:07:11.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.91,0:07:14.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这些文件里有没有混进我的信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.73,0:07:17.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.74,0:07:19.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.49,0:07:23.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.22,0:07:23.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.25,0:07:36.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别胡乱猜测
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.78,0:07:38.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.66,0:07:41.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说那家伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.85,0:07:50.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.97,0:07:52.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.01,0:07:53.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.94,0:07:54.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他会来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.45,0:07:56.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也没说不愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.66,0:07:58.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.88,0:08:01.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是一起去听音乐会而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.44,0:08:03.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是这样而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.03,0:08:05.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  是机会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.57,0:08:08.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢了  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.06,0:08:19.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,京都表扬我们很好地使用了红莲二式
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.83,0:08:20.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是感动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.04,0:08:22.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是被那个白色铠甲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.57,0:08:23.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要介意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.87,0:08:25.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,平手嘛  平手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.61,0:08:30.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙莉那家伙怎么了  那么突然
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.69,0:08:32.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸是去单身赴任
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.88,0:08:34.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是说要让我心情好一点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.88,0:08:36.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以总是会送这种东西给我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.00,0:08:38.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.84,0:08:39.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.37,0:08:41.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.34,0:08:42.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,情书
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.14,0:08:43.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.29,0:08:47.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙不吃玩笑这一套
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.65,0:08:48.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,玉城笑得太夸张了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.35,0:08:50.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,京都来的诏书
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.21,0:08:53.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说务必要和我们见面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.30,0:08:54.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是需要那么大惊小怪的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.13,0:08:56.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说大惊小怪  那可是京都啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.33,0:08:58.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果让他们承认的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.53,0:08:59.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他们也会提供我们资金援助
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.33,0:09:01.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们拮据的财政也会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.81,0:09:02.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,财政
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.66,0:09:06.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果按我计划的预算的话应该没问题才对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.30,0:09:08.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.76,0:09:09.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是我的错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.35,0:09:11.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已经是大组织了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.31,0:09:13.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,人数增加了可是预料之外的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.10,0:09:17.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要好好教导新人陪他们到处玩也是预料之外？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.45,0:09:18.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.35,0:09:19.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可知道哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.92,0:09:21.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们去了哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.88,0:09:22.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.84,0:09:26.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总而言之  会计的工作就交给扇了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.78,0:09:27.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.78,0:09:30.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从以前开始钱物管理就是交给我来做的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.81,0:09:31.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你想让人信任的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.43,0:09:33.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就给出相应的成果来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.99,0:09:35.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  你居然说我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.75,0:09:37.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这种说我们是同伴  还不给我们看脸的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.35,0:09:39.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底打算怎么样啊  ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.85,0:09:42.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下  这个么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.50,0:09:45.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO的真面目到底是什么不是问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.81,0:09:48.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO有让那个科奈莉娅防不胜防的实力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.64,0:09:50.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是我们黑色骑士团的首领啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.08,0:09:52.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你说还需要其他什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.58,0:10:12.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是妮娜…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.81,0:10:14.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你身体不舒服的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.68,0:10:16.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  什么也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.21,0:10:18.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.46,0:10:19.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  该怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.25,0:10:23.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  我们本来是直人的队伍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.76,0:10:25.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果妹妹卡莲都不介意的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.13,0:10:28.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为作为首领二代的你把位子让给他了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.67,0:10:29.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在成田的时候大家也
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.49,0:10:32.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那几乎可以说是胁迫了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.04,0:10:35.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对我们这些干部也保密
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.86,0:10:40.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有可能性的12个人已经掌握了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.19,0:10:43.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后就是如何出牌了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.07,0:10:46.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是需要即兴发挥吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.81,0:10:48.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.13,0:10:49.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.37,0:10:50.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.30,0:10:54.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才说了多管闲事的话  实在是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.97,0:10:58.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卡莲  你也想知道我的真实面目吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.90,0:11:03.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人  知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.26,0:11:09.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我告退了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.99,0:11:20.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.09,0:11:25.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,烧好像已经退了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.18,0:11:28.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可能只是想任性一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.55,0:11:29.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,任性？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.43,0:11:32.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最近总感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.69,0:11:36.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥好像要去很远的地方似的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.95,0:11:43.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以身体可能自然地配合了一下而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.45,0:11:46.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我发誓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.79,0:11:47.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.46,0:11:49.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,无论发生什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.77,0:11:51.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我总会在你的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.85,0:11:52.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.89,0:11:55.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  我可以说任性的话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.22,0:11:59.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请再握着我的手一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.83,0:12:01.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这样就睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.90,0:12:04.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得会再看见那个梦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.56,0:12:13.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你认真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.72,0:12:15.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想要拜托我事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.72,0:12:16.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.68,0:12:18.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,按照你给我的提示行动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.84,0:12:21.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,无论京都那边的意图为何
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.74,0:12:23.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我都想要得到那些人的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.23,0:12:25.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这是为了你的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.44,0:12:29.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了你生存的目的是需要的话  我可以帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.90,0:12:30.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.55,0:12:33.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,C.C.  我需要你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.44,0:12:37.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.91,0:12:39.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有  这是你忘了的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.04,0:12:42.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.73,0:12:44.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天不知道什么时候才能回来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.78,0:12:46.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打算给她打拒绝的电话而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.43,0:12:48.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要遵守约定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.53,0:12:52.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.40,0:12:54.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  正好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.05,0:12:55.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其实
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.45,0:12:56.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  鲁路
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.91,0:13:00.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,关于今天的约定  我说不定会迟到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.95,0:13:04.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  肯定没有问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.90,0:13:06.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会去的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.42,0:13:10.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,东京中央单轨铁路线  至成田
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.10,0:13:16.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把其他的干部也带来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.10,0:13:18.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,主人是这么吩咐的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.00,0:13:20.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了以防万一
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.68,0:13:21.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我让他们警戒周围的情况了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.51,0:13:23.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在就叫他们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.83,0:13:25.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是在此之前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.16,0:13:29.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,破坏较严重的尸体请送到第二帐篷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.89,0:13:30.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有遗物的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.75,0:13:31.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请尽快确认主人身份
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.28,0:13:34.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已确认身份的请送到第一帐篷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.67,0:13:36.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,并书面登记发现场所  时间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.47,0:13:39.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第二医疗班很快就会来帮忙…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.50,0:13:45.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的在吗  她  在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.47,0:13:47.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.57,0:13:50.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,忘掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.66,0:13:51.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,资料里她也不存在了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.62,0:13:56.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经满足了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.27,0:13:57.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尸体发掘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.52,0:14:01.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的话  我还是希望继续帮忙救援
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.41,0:14:04.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那在你死心之前请自便
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.89,0:14:07.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姑且也算是科奈莉娅殿下的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.74,0:14:10.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,罗伊德
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.15,0:14:14.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO…黑色骑士团到底想要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.12,0:14:16.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他们认为建筑在这牺牲之上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.42,0:14:17.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还能完成什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.53,0:14:19.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是正义的同伴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.23,0:14:21.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,用本人的话来说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.16,0:14:23.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是正义吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.76,0:14:24.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.44,0:14:28.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会想说『正义是什么』这种让人害臊的理论吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.59,0:14:31.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们姑且是军人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.16,0:14:36.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完成了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.79,0:14:38.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能源包的更换
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.88,0:14:39.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.05,0:14:49.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,塞希尔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.37,0:14:51.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我调查过了  纯血派他们的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.30,0:14:54.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.33,0:14:55.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对  是辐射波动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.28,0:14:58.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到居然协助敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.22,0:15:00.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个拉克夏塔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.90,0:15:02.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人的机师也是王牌级的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.09,0:15:05.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀精神不稳定的现在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.91,0:15:08.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果再次和这种对手战斗的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.22,0:15:09.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是想说赢不了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.11,0:15:11.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的Lancelot
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.88,0:15:16.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经过了很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.16,0:15:17.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还要开啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.28,0:15:19.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你倒是冷静一点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.76,0:15:20.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真丢脸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.81,0:15:22.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.90,0:15:25.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在上升
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.74,0:15:36.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,给你们带来不便了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.62,0:15:38.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,主人在等大家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.03,0:15:48.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里  富士矿山
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.13,0:15:50.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人的吧  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.78,0:15:52.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能到这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.66,0:15:53.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不会有错的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.28,0:15:55.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这座山  这个形状
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.02,0:15:58.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是说  这个下面有sakuradite
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.61,0:16:00.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诱发战争的罪魁祸首
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.81,0:16:03.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有入侵者  毫不迟疑就会被射杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.19,0:16:06.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到居然把势力延伸到这种地方来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.86,0:16:08.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,京都果然厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.35,0:16:09.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很丑恶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.76,0:16:12.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,过去曾经如此山清水秀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.66,0:16:16.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以水清澈  山碧绿的富饶而著称的灵峰富士山
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.52,0:16:19.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就如同现在已屈服在帝国之下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.51,0:16:24.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽仍生存但被不断凌辱的我们日本的姿态
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.59,0:16:26.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真令人哀叹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.25,0:16:30.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我为无法以真面目见你们而道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.17,0:16:34.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是ZERO  关于这点你也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.84,0:16:36.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能不看透
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.12,0:16:39.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你究竟是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.02,0:16:43.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让我看看吧  你的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.42,0:16:51.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.65,0:16:54.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO赐予了我们力量与胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.51,0:16:55.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.13,0:16:55.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.78,0:16:58.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,叫扇的是哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.57,0:16:59.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.26,0:16:59.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.36,0:17:02.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你把ZERO的假面拿下来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.32,0:17:09.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,扇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.40,0:17:10.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.94,0:17:12.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我也想相信  对你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.72,0:17:16.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  请让我相信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.46,0:17:20.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,女…女人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.87,0:17:21.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.75,0:17:22.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.59,0:17:24.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人不是ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.04,0:17:25.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我见过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.25,0:17:27.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她和ZERO在一起的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.49,0:17:29.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那里的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.15,0:17:31.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.23,0:17:31.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.43,0:17:35.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且你  不是日本人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.94,0:17:38.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,YES  京都的代表
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.04,0:17:40.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,桐原泰藏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.77,0:17:44.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能让知道大人真面目的人活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.42,0:17:46.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,更不用说她不是日本人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.09,0:17:47.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.04,0:17:49.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有关系啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.14,0:17:57.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是软弱啊  而且
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.93,0:17:59.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行为和思想都很陈腐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.46,0:18:03.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  你们才赢不了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.06,0:18:04.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.50,0:18:06.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.50,0:18:07.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.39,0:18:09.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,会被远隔操作射击到的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.92,0:18:11.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道吗  谁也不要动手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.52,0:18:14.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,桐原泰藏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.90,0:18:18.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姑且不论和sakuradite挖掘产业有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.46,0:18:20.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作为桐原产业的创建者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.79,0:18:23.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,枢木政权的影之建立者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.46,0:18:26.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  战败后摇身一变
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.23,0:18:28.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,积极地成为殖民地的协助者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.30,0:18:31.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,通称  卖国贼的桐原
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.30,0:18:34.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  他的真正身份
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.70,0:18:36.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是管理全国反抗者们的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.70,0:18:38.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,京都六家的重镇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.76,0:18:40.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,城府真深
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.40,0:18:41.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真不一般啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.50,0:18:43.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙  对大人的诽谤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.23,0:18:43.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,住口
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.59,0:18:47.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如您所猜测的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.82,0:18:50.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我  不是日本人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.08,0:18:52.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.46,0:18:55.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怪不得不能让我们看到脸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.06,0:18:59.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,既然不是日本人  为什么要战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.71,0:19:01.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底有什么企图
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.57,0:19:02.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,布里塔尼亚的崩溃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.41,0:19:04.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.23,0:19:06.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道能够实现吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.96,0:19:07.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你能做到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.37,0:19:08.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.41,0:19:10.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果问为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.62,0:19:13.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我有不得不完成这事的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.25,0:19:16.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是对手实在是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.26,0:19:19.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.15,0:19:21.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.62,0:19:22.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,桐原公
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.15,0:19:23.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.60,0:19:27.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,八年前被送到那家当牺牲品的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.04,0:19:28.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.09,0:19:30.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,当时无论如何承蒙照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.29,0:19:35.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果对手不是我的话你是不是打算把他当作人质
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.33,0:19:36.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.62,0:19:39.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对于我来说  只能做到提出我的愿望而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.51,0:19:44.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,八年前的种子开花了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.82,0:19:49.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,该死  看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.63,0:19:51.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,扇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.36,0:19:51.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.81,0:19:55.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人毫无疑问是布里塔尼亚的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.91,0:19:58.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,无法显示真正的面目我也能够理解了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.20,0:20:00.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我能够保证
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.89,0:20:02.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跟随ZERO吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.69,0:20:06.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,据点隐蔽或者情报搜寻这些我们也会协助
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.08,0:20:10.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,十分感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.09,0:20:12.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢  桐原公
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.86,0:20:16.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要踏上去吗  修罗之路
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.75,0:20:19.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果  这是我的命运的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.25,0:20:23.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第2  第5  第7  第8  第9小队
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.02,0:20:26.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在管理总部的指挥下继续独自作业
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.21,0:20:28.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,菲奈特之后是这儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.57,0:20:30.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,遗骸是那具
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.01,0:20:33.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  因为是这种情况
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.69,0:20:34.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.09,0:20:36.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么请您确认
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.95,0:20:46.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然已经不在了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.10,0:20:57.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎么样从现在开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.03,0:21:02.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,黑色骑士团真正成为如我所愿而行动的组织了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.95,0:21:12.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  对不起我迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.97,0:21:14.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为你已经走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.37,0:21:18.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  先不管那些
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.39,0:21:21.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总而言之先找个避雨的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.38,0:21:23.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  鲁路
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.97,0:21:27.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO是弱者的朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.16,0:21:29.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.78,0:21:30.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.37,0:21:35.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  为什么杀了我爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.88,0:21:39.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸  很温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.57,0:21:42.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都从没有打过我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.36,0:21:45.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么坏事都没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.70,0:21:47.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  被活埋了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.00,0:21:50.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,无法呼吸的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.76,0:21:51.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.27,0:21:53.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么爸爸要死
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.99,0:21:56.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.72,0:21:57.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.07,0:21:59.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.89,0:22:05.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你  鲁路
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.52,0:22:08.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,帮帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.43,0:23:51.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.87,0:23:52.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行动的结果这种
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.65,0:23:55.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  我是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.64,0:23:56.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.32,0:23:58.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从舞台上消失很简单
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.30,0:24:00.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要舍弃ZERO这个存在就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.40,0:24:02.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要堵住桐原的嘴巴
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.01,0:24:05.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就能恢复鲁路修·兰佩洛奇
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.02,0:24:07.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  可是
